{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8fe87ccbfb","title":"贺美国共产党三十周年电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6ea100b2e4","index":0,"year":1949,"month":8,"day":23,"articleId":"8fe87ccbfb"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"2261564541","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"8fe87ccbfb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽东代表中共中央致电美国共产党中央主席福斯特，祝贺美国共产党成立三十周年。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6d1826de00","type":"title","text":"贺美国共产党三十周年电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"8fe87ccbfb"},{"id":"2261564541","type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的福斯特同志和值尼斯同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"8fe87ccbfb"},{"id":"5a5dd2d598","type":"paragraph","text":"我们中国共产党人和中国劳动人民热烈庆祝美国共产党的三十周年。美国共产党和美国进步分子，在美国反动势力高压之下，为着国际和平，为着美国工人和美国人民的民主权利，为着中美人民的真诚友谊，坚持不屈不绕的奋斗，对于中国人民和世界各国人民都是一个重要的鼓励和援助。美国的未来，不属于外强中干的美国反动势力，而属于你们和美国人民。庆祝你们和美国人民的蚕斗得到成功，庆祝中美两国工人阶级和两国人民的团结继续增强。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"8fe87ccbfb"},{"id":"b82d1769f7","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党中央委员会主席毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"8fe87ccbfb"},{"id":"1cd3f4ea8a","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年八月二十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"8fe87ccbfb"}],"page":{"id":"90fd460087","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"8fe87ccbfb","start":160,"end":160}}}},"__N_SSG":true}